---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="How HonestPickReview uses affiliate links and how that relates to our editorial ratings.">
  <div class="container" style="padding-top: 24px;">
    <p class="breadcrumbs"><a href="/">Home</a> / Affiliate Disclosure</p>
  </div>
  <article class="container prose" style="max-width: 720px; padding-bottom: 48px;">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p>
      HonestPickReview.com participates in affiliate marketing programs, which means we may earn a commission
      on qualifying purchases made through links on this site, at no additional cost to you.
    </p>
    <h2>What This Means</h2>
    <p>
      When you click a "Check Current Price" or similar outbound link and make a purchase, the retailer may
      pay us a small commission. This is a common way independent review sites are able to operate without
      charging readers directly.
    </p>
    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
    <p>
      Affiliate relationships do not influence which products we choose to review or how we rate them. Our
      ratings are based on the research process described on our <a href="/how-we-review/">How We Review</a>
      page, applied consistently regardless of whether a commission is available on a given product.
    </p>
    <h2>Questions</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this disclosure, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
